<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Aplicaci贸n de Recetas</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg-color: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15, 32, 39, 0.8), rgba(32, 58, 67, 0.8), rgba(44, 83, 100, 0.8));
        --text-color: #ffffff;
        --form-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        --form-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        --form-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        --button-bg: linear-gradient(90deg, #9c0720, #610000);
        --button-hover-bg: linear-gradient(90deg, #610000, #9c0720);
        --button-shadow: rgba(156, 7, 32, 0.5);
        --link-color: #ffffff;
        --link-hover-color: #f1666d;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        background: var(--bg-color), url('/src/assets/img/saludable.jpg');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-blend-mode: overlay; /* Combina el degradado con la imagen */
        color: var(--text-color);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
        overflow: hidden;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
      }

      .background-design {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: var(--bg-color);
        z-index: 0;
        opacity: 0.9;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--text-color);
        text-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        color: rgba(224, 247, 250, 0.8);
        animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
      }

      .options {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        animation: fadeIn 3s ease-in-out;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 15px 40px;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: var(--text-color);
        background: var(--button-bg);
        border: none;
        border-radius: 30px;
        text-decoration: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px var(--button-shadow);
      }

      .button:hover {
        background: var(--button-hover-bg);
        color: var(--text-color);
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px var(--button-shadow);
      }

      .card {
        background: var(--form-bg);
        border: 1px solid var(--form-border);
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px var(--form-shadow);
        padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 400px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      @keyframes fadeIn {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: scale(0.9);
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: scale(1);
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="background-design"></div>
    <div class="card">
      <h1>Bienvenido a la Aplicaci贸n de Recetas</h1>
      <p>Explora las mejores recetas y crea tu propia colecci贸n</p>
      <div class="options">
        <a href="/login" class="button">Iniciar Sesi贸n</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>